{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"为朱光题词","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为朱光题词\""},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到南方去，同原在南方工作的同志团结在一起，将南方工作做好，这是我的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱光同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1949年8月，朱光奉命南下广州，参加广州的接管工作。朱光离开东北，进关南下途经北平时，来到中南海。朱德应朱光之请，即席书写了一帧《赠友人》诗相赠。尔后，朱光又应毛泽东之请，到其书房叙谈，毛泽东亲笔为朱光题词一幅。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":119,"page_end":119},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}